  "title": "Lounge Assistant - Airport Lounge",
  "description": "<p>Accor is in a partnership with one of the World's Leading Airlines, to manage the Lounge operations located in Changi Airport.</p><p>The role of a Lounge Attendant is to perform assigned cleaning tasks efficiently, ensuring high standards of cleanliness and presentation are consistently met. This role is crucial in contributing to a positive guest experience by maintaining a spotless and welcoming lounge environment that exceeds expectations.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Keep tables, chairs and service areas clean and tidy </li><li>General cleaning of Airport Transit Lounge </li><li>Take responsibility for your designated section and station</li><li>Carry out programmed / regular cleaning duties as allocated</li><li>Assist guest with directions and request</li></ul><p><u><strong>Qualifications</strong></u></p><ul><li>Prior related experience preferably in hospitality or airline lounge </li></ul><p><strong>Additional Information:</strong></p><ul><li>5 day work week</li><li>44 hours per week</li><li>Eligible for overtime allowances</li><li>Uniform and training provide</li><li>Competitive benefits</li><li>Travel-related perks.</li><li>Uniforms provided.</li><li>Training and career development opportunities.</li><li>Supportive and multicultural work environment.</li></ul>",
