    "description": "<p>Accor is the world's leading hotel operator, present in 92 countries with more than 3,500 hotels and 450,000 rooms. With more than 160,000 employees in Accor brand hotels worldwide, the Group offers to its clients and partners nearly 45 years of know-how and expertise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Asia Pacific, Accor is the market leader, with over 550 hotels and nearly 106,000 rooms in 16 countries – Australia, New Zealand, Fiji, French Polynesia, Cambodia, China, India, Indonesia, Japan, Korea, Laos, Malaysia, Philippines, Singapore, Thailand and Vietnam.  In addition, more than 200 hotels are scheduled to open over the next three years.</p>\r\n",
